      <body><div><pb facs="#facs_" n="" xml:id="img_NaN"/>
            <ab facs="#facs__eSc_dummyblock_">
              <p>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_dc3045ff">Dear Ben,</l>
              </p>
              <p>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_b57eef3d">My letter also was written very hastily. We have been very</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_32fc9588">subject to air raids. Five bombers almost crashed into this house,</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_86ef664b">They just missed; but I find it <choice>
                  <sic>diffiult</sic>
                  <corr>difficult</corr>
                </choice> to concentrate; and</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_66f5bcc7">no doubt misinterpreted what you said.  though I didnt mean to.</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_abb288f2">To be frank, I doubt if I've got your meaning in your last letter.</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_e00fb498">But I would like to understand your point of view and if possible</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_90e7292a">make clear my own; so I answer, in the hope <choice>
                  <sic>thta</sic>
                  <corr>that</corr>
                </choice> the <choice>
                  <sic>iren</sic>
                  <corr>[iron?]</corr>
                </choice> will remain</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_288e0edc">silent.</l>
              </p>
              <p>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_9bf5e8e9">You say you dont wish any one to give up painting writing or</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_1b0f5519">thinking about art and <choice>
                  <sic>litetrure</sic>
                  <corr>literature</corr>
                </choice>. <del hand="typewriter">But for some reason Roger Fry</del></l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_c2f9873b"><del hand="typewriter">did this in the wrong way.</del> You mean to go on doing it yourself</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_3168ae2c">when the wars over. My <choice>
                  <sic> uarrel</sic>
                  <corr>quarrel</corr>
                </choice> <choice>
                  <sic>yoy</sic>
                  <corr>you</corr>
                </choice> say is not with art but with</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_c0d8bfcf">Bloomsbury." But what is Bloomsbury? It means, as far as I can see,</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_00fca6fc">a set of people vho sat on the floor at Bernard Street</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_4032d809">saying "more and more I understand nothing of humanity in the mass</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_e12ca8e4">and were content with that instead of trying to make <choice>
                  <sic>h manity</sic>
                  <corr>humanity</corr>
                </choice> in the</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_d36cda3f">mass understand and appreciate what you knew and saw"</l>
              </p>
              <p>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_d8e6a36f">Who is "you" in that passage? <del>Do you mean</del> I take it that you mean</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_44e43f5d">me in the first place; and to that I reply, I never said anything</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_41c7f0ae">of the kind. I quoted Rogers saying; I also quoted his saying,</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_de83ada4">Am I responsible for all that Roger said Then I am also responsible</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_949a2a88">for his saying, More and more [I] dread <choice>
                  <sic>impirsonment</sic>
                  <corr>imprisonment</corr>
                </choice> <del hand="typewriter">in the</del></l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_36a983d6">the imprisonment of <choice>
                  <sic>egotims</sic>
                  <corr>egotism</corr>
                </choice>; I am also responsible for</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_6181bbf5">teaching the elementary school children [in] the black country</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_03221e24">how to draw. I am also responsible for his attempt to make art</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_7ed7033a">enjoyed by the <choice>
                  <sic> ublic</sic>
                  <corr>public</corr>
                </choice> in Southwark. In fact I am not</l>
               <l facs="#facs__eSc_line_bf4b138b">any thing Roger did or said. About 150 was spent on my education.</l>
              </p>
